  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6556527">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6556527/" class="title-link">对于研究中国战史的重要工具书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6556527"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/33561058/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u33561058-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/33561058/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">灰云天</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-02-21"
      class="main-meta">2014-02-21 09:52:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6556527_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        编者参阅了大量的历史资料。应该说比我们个人能够看到的资料要全的多，可以省去我们直接翻阅、整理历史典籍的时间。      可能因为是台湾编的，大部分内容又是直接从史籍中引用，书中语言是半文言和文言结合的，可能不习惯看文言的读者会有些阅读困难。       强烈建议开...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6556527_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6556527_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7598811">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7598811/" class="title-link">波澜壮阔的战争史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7598811"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4873696/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4873696-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4873696/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">再快乐一点</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-14"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-14 14:01:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7598811_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1年多的时间里，终于看完了 很耗费心血的一套书，特别是图集，非常赞 改日要在家里收藏一套。 对于中国军事地理，有了深入的了解  非常赞的书，稍微提一点点批评意见 1，部分内容详略不得当吧，篇幅和战事规模不成比例，可能与资料有关。明代抗日援朝之战、甲午战争，篇幅很大...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
